cast.original_title: バイオハザード ヴェンデッタ
cast.overview: BSAA Chris Redfield enlists the help of government agent Leon S. Kennedy and Professor Rebecca Chambers from Alexander Institute of Biotechnology to stop a death merchant with a vengeance from spreading a deadly virus in New York.
cast.title: Resident Evil: Vendetta

cast.overview: With the impending ice age almost upon them, a mismatched trio of prehistoric critters – Manny the woolly mammoth, Diego the saber-toothed tiger and Sid the giant sloth – find an orphaned infant and decide to return it to its human parents. Along the way, the unlikely allies become friends but, when enemies attack, their quest takes on far nobler aims.
cast.title: Ice Age

cast.overview: After the vicious slaughter of his family by stone-cold mercenary Sub-Zero, Hanzo Hasashi is exiled to the torturous Netherrealm. There, in exchange for his servitude to the sinister Quan Chi, he’s given a chance to avenge his family – and is resurrected as Scorpion, a lost soul bent on revenge. Back on Earthrealm, Lord Raiden gathers a team of elite warriors – Shaolin monk Liu Kang, Special Forces officer Sonya Blade and action star Johnny Cage – an unlikely band of heroes with one chance to save humanity. To do this, they must defeat Shang Tsung’s horde of Outworld gladiators and reign over the Mortal Kombat tournament.
cast.title: Mortal Kombat Legends: Scorpion's Revenge

cast.overview: A boy is given the ability to become an adult superhero in times of need with a single magic word.
cast.title: Shazam!

cast.overview: When the Flash finds himself dropped into the middle of World War II, he joins forces with Wonder Woman and her top-secret team known as the Justice Society of America.
cast.title: Justice Society: World War II

details.biography:
Darin De Paul is an American voice actor known for his video game performances as Dr. Samuel Hayden/Seraphim in Doom and Doom Eternal, Reinhardt in Overwatch and Overwatch 2, Ardyn Izunia in Final Fantasy XV, Revenant in Apex Legends, Emperor Valkorion in Star Wars: The Old Republic, and J. Jonah Jameson in the Marvel’s Spider-Man series.
